Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think this is a good thing, as it fosters a sense of community, helps build social skills, and exposes you to people you might never have met otherwise.  it also builds a greater connection to the school and to the campus itself, meaning it helps the school as much as it helps the students.